Supporting scripts to run and evaluate RandAL
---------------------------------------------

1. do_exps.py
Python script to test RandAL with multiple simulated datasets:

Usage:  python do_exps.py -r ref -l read_len -e error_rate -o result_file_name
For example: python do_exps.py -r Stap -r Dros -l 35 -l 51 -e 0.02 -e 0.04 -o overall_results.txt

2. wgsim_eval.pl
Perl script to evaluate a SAM output and then produce result to screen. Original code from https://github.com/lh3/wgsim.

3. wgsim_eval_tofile.pl
Perl script to evaluate a SAM ouput and then write results (including error mapped reads) to files, used in the do_exps.py Python script. Modified from wgsim_eval.pl.